comments: Brissett (IND) extends his arm into Quickley's (NYK) body and holds Quickley's arm, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Quickley (NYK) makes clean contact with the ball as he attempts to tie up Brissett (IND).
Barrett (NYK) jumps  verticality and absorbs the contact from Mathurin (IND) that occurs prior to Robinson (NYK) cleanly  blocking Mathurin's driving shot attempt.
Robinson (NYK) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Indiana.
Brissett (IND) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Robinson (NYK) is retreating his arms into a vertical position and marginal contact occurs with Brissett (IND) prior to Robinson and Grimes (NYK) making clean contact with the ball.
Nesmith (IND) moves slightly forward towards Barrett (NYK) and marginal contact occurs as Mathurin (IND) simultaneously dislodges the ball from Barrett.
Nesmith (IND) lowers his hand and makes contact with Barrett's (NYK) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Nembhard (IND) legally contests Quickley's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Barrett (NYK) extends both hands forward and initiates contact with Nesmith (IND) that affects his SQBR.
Quickley (NYK) brings his hand forward towards Jackson (IND) and marginal contact occurs as Jackson pursues the rebound.
Nesmith (IND) avoids making contact with Quickley's (NYK) arm as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Nembhard (IND) jumps alongside of Robinson's (NYK) path and marginal body contact occurs during the shot near the rim.
Jackson (IND) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to New York.
Quickley (NYK) commits a take foul on Brissett (IND).
Brissett (IND) is moving alongside Quickley's (NYK) path and absorbs the marginal contact as he cleanly blocks Quickley's shot attempt.

Brissett (IND) makes contact with the ball while part of the ball is inside the imaginary cylinder above the basket ring.  After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court (defensive goaltending) was confirmed.
Brissett (IND) legally contests Quickley's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Jackson (IND) makes contact with the ball and dislodges the ball as simultaneous incidental arm contact occurs with Robinson (NYK).
Toppin (NYK) commits a take foul on Nesmith (IND).
Barrett (NYK) commits a take foul on Nembhard (IND).
